{"tid":1238115,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"21/6假如真係升級 實際行動討論區","createTime":"2019-06-17T16:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T04:52:12.000Z","uid":203499,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8eeeae99228a0b56b1f2be02fe386a6c18a2b329","tid":1238115,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:54:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 想問下deadline係20號晏晝5點定係夜晚11點？</span><br />\n有巴打解答話firm左5點<br />\n但我暫時未揾到sauce<br />\n麻煩大家再double check<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdaXU0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdaXU0j.png&h=b569d956&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpqkSM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpqkSM0.png&h=d2e1525c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 行動升級具體係點？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.1 根據上圖，包圍政總</span><br />\n唔係話想潑大家冷水<br />\n但根據12號經驗<br />\n我地同癲狗裝備差距實在太大<br />\n當日未出水砲 音波砲已經清到場<br />\n個人覺得死守難度頗高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.2 二百萬人，兵分三路</span><br />\n星期日遊行記錄就有二百萬人<br />\n但21號係星期五<br />\n仲要係全日戰<br />\n一定有好多人番工不了<br />\n參考番12號嘅經驗<br />\n高峰時期目測大概有幾萬人<br />\n中午12點1點會少人啲<br />\n<br />\n我唔係支持大家番工不了<br />\n但現實啲諗<br />\n我地最起碼要研究點樣撐到放工時間等支援<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.3 行動形式</span><br />\n之前有睇過位巴打分享<br />\n人少打死守的確冇優勢<br />\n反而可以考慮下快閃遊擊<br />\n或者其他可取之道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.4 實際安排</span><br />\n屆時係咪參照番12號咁<br />\n分別設立物資站 急救站 前線 後援等等？<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n以上全部都係發夢夢到嘅一隅之見<br />\n各位喺唔互屌分化嘅情況下<br />\n歡迎理性討論 交流意見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，加油！</span>"},{"pid":"cf703340fc6c96a8614da0a14b64b9110ae4ecbd","tid":1238115,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">最新消息</span><br />\n<br />\nDeadline已確定係晏晝5點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nm64z2x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNm64z2x.png&h=166078cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人，約定你</span>"},{"pid":"36841fe06c293172430f3e652e2986c7af4169d4","tid":1238115,"uid":68604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家做野！！！！！<br />\nSPREAD！！！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f14151a862d0c38c0a5aedee1194483d0e6b707a","tid":1238115,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"奉公守法,向警察舉報身邊罪行<br />\n請勿用999,為保障個人私隱,請自行匿名隱性<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2Fcontact_us.html&d=7EcP4%2BvGpl6inSsjOqiUXgTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=79357ba4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html</a>"},{"pid":"053245476b3772e5e98ef7376199c1970cd4d8b9","tid":1238115,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"屌 認真po比人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e322a7e3fc0d117afb0031b62e17d8e8986fc815","tid":1238115,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"推推，認真文"},{"pid":"450f264044ad742e90a7b790b8ebd31228797e46","tid":1238115,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e322a7e3fc0d117afb0031b62e17d8e8986fc815","tid":1238115,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"推推，認真文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c714532c4985d6c572e49e86d8bf2e09911b8fcd","tid":1238115,"uid":203499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T17:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae6f4ef6d4c115909b0d474ec66124